Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.47,0:12:52.18,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 1,0:12:52.18,0:12:54.01,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,安曇さん　中学生でしょ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.18,0:12:54.01,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,安昙  你是初中生吧
